oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - NewTown - 2013-11-09
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by the musical group NewTown as part of the Bluegrass and Beyond program from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on November 9, 2013. Second performance of four. Presented by the Crump family and Cotten Music Center. Honoring George A. and Marjorie S. Crump.
